dct_title_s: Terra Firma et Novum Regnum Granatense et Popayan
dct_description_sm: Publication information in Spanish. Shows parts of Panama, Colombia, and Venezuela. Prime meridian: [Ferro]. Relief shown pictorially. "Descripción del mapa: Terra Firma, Nuevo Reyno de Granada y Popayán (apr. Panamá, Colombia, Venezuela). Original de 1647."
